folder: Newport Street & Rockaway Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Newport Street, east from Rockaway Ave., showing in the center a 5-story
building, which is P.S. No. 164.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

=======================================

THAT'S P.S. 184, NOT 164
